            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To isolate the 1 min Br-86+Br-87 activity the irradia-",
                "tion time was chosen sufficiently short (150 sec) to",
                "avoid the accumulation of longer-lived bromine isotopes",
